  <name>Friday Night Funkin'</name>
  <summary>Indie rhythm game developed by the Funkin' Crew (Unofficial).</summary>
  <description>
    <p>This is a unofficial Flatpak version of Friday night funkin', i am unafilliated with the Funkin' Crew inc.</p>
    <p>yo really think so?</p>
    <p>What is there even in this game?</p>
    <ul>
      <li>8 main weeks</li>
      <li>Erect Remixes for most songs</li>
      <li>Pico Mixes for some songs</li>
      <li>Funky graphics</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
